# AgentGate live-provider proof credentials
#
# This file is only for local testing. It is gitignored.
# Fill in whichever providers you want to validate, then run:
#   pnpm live:openai
#   pnpm live:anthropic
#   pnpm live:mcp
#   pnpm live:matrix
#
# OpenAI note:
# OpenAI live proof can use either:
# 1) a logged-in Codex session (`codex login`) for the subscription-style tandem path, or
# 2) OPENAI_API_KEY for the lower-level Responses API path.
OPENAI_API_KEY=
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-5.4

# Anthropic note:
# Anthropic live proof can use either:
# 1) ANTHROPIC_API_KEY for the SDK path, or
# 2) a logged-in Claude Code session (`claude auth login` or `claude setup-token`)
#    for the Claude Code tandem path.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-3-5-sonnet-latest
